                    "difficulty": "Easy",
                    "answer": "1",
                    "question_type": 1,
                    "question": "设 $P(A)=P(B)=\\frac{1}{4}, P(C)=\\frac{1}{2}, P(A B)=0, P(A C)=P(B C)=\\frac{1}{8}$, 则 $A, B, C$ 三者都不发生的概率 $P(\\bar{A} \\cdot \\bar{B} \\cdot \\bar{C})=$ ( ).",
                    "analysis": "考虑 $A, B, C$ 三者都不发生的逆事件为“三者至少发生一个”，即 $A \\cup B \\cup C$。由于 $A B C \\subset A B$，且 $P(AB)=0$，所以 $P(A B C)=0$。根据概率的加法公式：\n$$\n\\begin{aligned}\nP(A \\cup B \\cup C) &= P(A)+P(B)+P(C)-P(A B)-P(A C)-P(B C)+P(A B C) \\\\\n&= \\frac{1}{4}+\\frac{1}{4}+\\frac{1}{2}-0-\\frac{1}{8}-\\frac{1}{8}+0=\\frac{3}{4}\n\\end{aligned}\n$$\n所以\n$$\nP(\\bar{A} \\cdot \\bar{B} \\cdot \\bar{C}) = P(\\overline{A \\cup B \\cup C}) = 1-P(A \\cup B \\cup C) = 1 - \\frac{3}{4} = \\frac{1}{4}.\n$$\n注意：$0 \\leq P(A B C) \\leq P(A B)=0 \\Rightarrow P(A B C)=0$。",
